library(rpart)
library(caret)

library(lattice)

ucla <- read.csv('http://stats.idre.ucla.edu/stat/data/binary.csv')
ucla$admit= factor(ucla$admit)

set.seed(2021)
ucla_index <- createDataPartition(ucla$admit, p= 0.8, list=F)
ucla_train <- ucla[ucla_index, ]
ucla_test <- ucla[-ucla_index, ]
